package StatusEffect
import StatusEffectInstance

/**
Abstract Bonus class that can be inherited by your own bonuses.
Requires to implement one method that takes unit and modifies it.
*/
public abstract class StatusEffect

    /**
    this method should never by called manually!
    Let Status handle this instead.
    If implemented in child class it must return BonusInstance to allow bonus removing
    */
    abstract function applyBonus(unit u) returns StatusEffectInstance